    {
      "avalancheActivity": {
        "comment": "Na h\u0159ebenech Krkono\u0161 je 50 - 70 cm sn\u011bhu.  Na krustu napadlo za posledn\u00ed sn\u011b\u017een\u00ed 11 cm nov\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu v kombinaci se S v\u011btrem. \r\nB\u011bhem dne se budou teploty pohybovat pod 0\u00b0C. Na z\u00e1v\u011btrnn\u00fdch svaz\u00edch se mohou vyskytnout laviny z nav\u00e1t\u00e9ho sn\u011bhu (JV, J a JZ).\r\nUvoln\u011bn\u00ed laviny je mo\u017en\u00e9 jen p\u0159i velk\u00e9m dodate\u010dn\u00e9m zat\u00ed\u017een\u00ed a to jen ojedin\u011ble ve velmi strm\u00e9m extr\u00e9mn\u00edm ter\u00e9nu. Je mo\u017enost samovoln\u00e9ho uvoln\u011bn\u00ed mal\u00fdch, nebo st\u0159edn\u00edch lavin, kter\u00e9 se v\u011bt\u0161inou zastav\u00ed je\u0161t\u011b na svahu.\r\n\r\nTendence lavinov\u00e9ho nebezpe\u010d\u00ed je setrval\u00e1."
